	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>
	<p><strong>The Bankruptcy search provides access to a listing of personal and business bankruptcy filings from 50 states, District of Columbia, Guam, Puerto Rico, Virgin Islands, Mariana Islands, and Upper Marianna Islands. All US Bankruptcy District Courts are contained in this listing. Date coverage may vary depending on the District Court. Information is updated Daily; Monday through Friday, except holidays.</strong></p>

	<p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p style="font-style:oblique;">For optimal results, include Full Name &amp; Address &amp; SSN or Full Name &amp; Address in your search terms.</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>

        <p>Search results may only be viewed for a single subject. If insufficient criteria are utilized to narrow the search to your subject, a list of matches to your input will be displayed. Select the appropriate subject from the list to view the Bankruptcy information.</p>
